WEBVTT

00:10:00.440 --> 00:10:05.776
I am amazed to see how volunteers,

00:10:05.800 --> 00:10:09.936
individuals, parents,
teachers, school principals,

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:11.456
have come together

00:10:11.480 --> 00:10:15.736
and taken this menstrual awareness
drive to their own communities,

00:10:15.760 --> 00:10:19.456
have made sure that the girls
learn about periods at the right age

00:10:19.480 --> 00:10:21.640
and helped in breaking this taboo.

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:27.336
I dream of a future
where menstruation is not a curse,

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:28.896
not a disease,

00:10:28.920 --> 00:10:31.360
but a welcoming change in a girl's life.